  "texts": [
    "An accuracy of greater than 0.95 was attained using this method (Pydipati et al. 2006).",
    "The following techniques may be employed to discern the presence of these pathogens, which have the potential to infiltrate various plant parts such as stems, vegetables, fruits, and more:",
    "• Identifying and classifying the diseases.",
    "• Determining the affected region.",
    "• Retrieving the affected area's feature set."
  ]
